{"tid":2442588,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"徐德義拒認指引不足　反指已提醒市民打針前可先諮詢醫生","createTime":"2021-03-11T12:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T12:33:15.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e9c2f310a622d2be76528f6c86dab481c2354488","tid":2442588,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/844kDzdIm8zUjhSYND1ed_iNGbM=/1024x576/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3HQRPYOJ5VBCNCRAUHOVGU7AXM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F844kDzdIm8zUjhSYND1ed_iNGbM%3D%2F1024x576%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3HQRPYOJ5VBCNCRAUHOVGU7AXM.png&h=6b56cc51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食物及衞生局副局長徐德義在疫情記者會上，強調接種疫苗屬「個人選擇」，又指在預約接種時已提供不少資料予市民參考。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n近日有多宗懷疑接種疫苗後感不適個案，更有4人在打完科興後死亡，政府被批評相關指引不足，未有列明不應接種的群組。食物及衞生局副局長徐德義在疫情記者會上，被多次質問仍未有承認不足，雖指會發佈更詳細指引，惟強調接種疫苗屬「個人選擇」，並反指在預約接種時已提供不少資料予市民參考，更已列明長期病患者應先諮詢醫生意見。<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局副局長徐德義出席疫情記者會時指出，過去一周有51宗確診個案，包括22宗不明源頭，逾13萬人已接種疫苗。他呼籲不論是接種哪一種疫苗，市民都要閱讀疫苗須知，如果對任何疫苗曾有過敏就不要接種，如有慢性疾病或者其他不確定情況，應先諮詢家庭醫生意見，或在到門診覆診時接種。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210311/KAKCVNM5YBGKZC6CGN6MWH5PIU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210311%2FKAKCVNM5YBGKZC6CGN6MWH5PIU%2F&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHRY%2Fip2Wc62AYORpdIbS17M%3D&h=27d1fbf5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210311%2FKAKCVNM5YBGKZC6CGN6MWH5PIU%2F&h=7d55f31e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210311/KAKCVNM5YBGKZC6CGN6MWH5PIU/</a>"},{"pid":"a046d68bc35e97b9b3c9d17338d4c1299c9e6fbb","tid":2442588,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:31:06.000Z","msg":"責任全在_方"},{"pid":"c2cf7f0d6d97c7fcc246ad6